commit.message:
builtins-1-le.c: Filter out gimple folding disabled message.

	* gcc.target/powerpc/builtins-1-le.c: Filter out gimple folding disabled
	message.  Fix scan-assembler patterns.

From-SVN: r258825

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@
+2018-03-23  Peter Bergner  <bergner@vnet.ibm.com>
+
+	* gcc.target/powerpc/builtins-1-le.c: Filter out gimple folding disabled
+	message.  Fix scan-assembler patterns.
+
 2018-03-23  Jakub Jelinek  <jakub@redhat.com>
 
 	PR c++/85015

@@ -1,6 +1,7 @@
 /* { dg-do compile { target { powerpc64le-*-* } } } */
 /* { dg-skip-if "do not override -mcpu" { powerpc*-*-* } { "-mcpu=*" } { "-mcpu=power8" } } */
-/* { dg-options "-mcpu=power8 -O0 -mno-fold-gimple" } */
+/* { dg-options "-mcpu=power8 -O0 -mno-fold-gimple -dp" } */
+/* { dg-prune-output "gimple folding of rs6000 builtins has been disabled." } */
 
 /* Test that a number of newly added builtin overloads are accepted
    by the compiler.  */
